    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3205500/extras/ee646a1e9025b52aae052be64beebf41.poster.avif?t=1759496699\" width=620 height=242 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3205500/extras/ee646a1e9025b52aae052be64beebf41.webm?t=1759496699\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3205500/extras/ee646a1e9025b52aae052be64beebf41.mp4?t=1759496699\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore a Digital World where you can collect and train creatures to build your ultimate team. Defend your upgradeable basement from waves of enemy attacks and strategically manage your resources to achieve evolutions. Travel through time to uncover the secret to prevent the impending Armageddon.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Improve Your Team</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Manage resources to unlock new evolutions for your creatures, perform special summoning rituals and create your strongest team.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3205500/extras/976fd45ac5a2a5fdc6e0d16b764d574b.poster.avif?t=1759496699\" width=620 height=242 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3205500/extras/976fd45ac5a2a5fdc6e0d16b764d574b.webm?t=1759496699\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3205500/extras/976fd45ac5a2a5fdc6e0d16b764d574b.mp4?t=1759496699\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Collect Creatures</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Defeat wild enemies to get their eggs that hatch into allies! Each creature brings unique abilities to your team, adding new evolution lines and endless possibilities. Build your dream squad and defeat evil bosses in the Digital World!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3205500/extras/b8f009f358c0aad4bfb2f72dda9111dc.poster.avif?t=1759496699\" width=620 height=242 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3205500/extras/b8f009f358c0aad4bfb2f72dda9111dc.webm?t=1759496699\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3205500/extras/b8f009f358c0aad4bfb2f72dda9111dc.mp4?t=1759496699\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Upgrade Your Basement</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As you advance, you can transform your basement into a place where your units can get the best equipment, buffs, unlock abilities and items to help  lin your adventure.</p>",
